org.eclipse.ecf.presence
Interface IRosterSubscribeListener

public interface IRosterSubscribeListener

Listener for handling notifications of subscribe/unsubscribe requests. Implementers of this interface must be registered via IPresenceContainerAdapter.addRosterSubscribeListener(IRosterSubscribeListener)

See Also:
IPresenceContainerAdapter
